  <brief_title>A Study of Avastin in Combination With Chemotherapy for Treatment of Colorectal Cancer and Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (ARIES)</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARIES</acronym>
  <official_title>An Observational Study of Avastin (Bevacizumab) in Combination With Chemotherapy for Treatment of Metastatic or Locally Advanced and Unresectable Colorectal Cancer and Locally Advanced or Metastatic Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (Excluding Predominant Squamous Cell Histology)</official_title>
