  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational study designed to follow patients with metastatic or locally
      advanced and unresectable CRC or locally advanced or metastatic NSCLC (excluding predominant
      squamous histology) who are receiving Avastin in combination with first-line chemotherapy.
      Second-line metastatic CRC patients are also eligible. Patients who started their Avastin
      containing therapy &lt;4 months prior to enrollment are eligible.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
